{"parse":{"title":"soh","pageid":38964,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"{{also|Soh|SOH|␁}}\n==Translingual==\n\n===Symbol===\n{{mul-symbol}}\n\n# {{ISO 639|3}}\n\n===See also===\n* {{langcat}}\n\n==English==\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{IPA|en|/səʊ/|a=UK}}\n* {{IPA|en|/soʊ/|a=US}}\n* {{rhymes|en|əʊ|s=1}}\n* {{homophones|en|seau|so|soe|;|sew|sow<aa:toe-tow>}} {{q|sense 2}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun}}\n\n# {{lb|en|music}} {{alt form|en|so}}.\n\n===Anagrams===\n* {{anagrams|en|a=hos|HOS|Hos.|OHS|OHs|Osh|SHO|Sho|hos|ohs|osh|sho|sho'}}\n\n==Acehnese==\n{{cardinalbox|ace||0|1||sa}}\n\n===Etymology===\nFrom {{inh|ace|cmc-pro|*sɔːh}}, a loan from {{bor|ace|aav}}. Compare {{cog|mkh-pro|*suəh||empty}}, {{cog|cjm|ꨧꨯꨱꩍ|tr=saoh}}.\n\n===Numeral===\n{{head|ace|num}}\n\n# [[zero]]\n\n===Adjective===\n{{head|ace|adj}}\n\n# [[empty]]\n\n==Gothic==\n\n===Romanization===\n{{got-rom|head=sōh}}\n\n# {{romanization of|got|𐍃𐍉𐌷}}\n\n==Pnar==\n\n===Etymology===\nFrom {{inh|pbv|aav-khs-pro|*sɔʔ}}. Cognate with {{cog|kha|soh}}.\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{IPA|pbv|/sɔʔ/}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{head|pbv|noun}}\n\n# [[fruit]]\n\n==Zhuang==\n\n===Etymology===\nFrom {{inh|za|tai-pro|*zɤːᴮ||straight}}. Cognate with {{cog|th|ซื่อ}}, {{cog|nod|ᨪᩨ᩵}}, {{cog|kkh|ᨪᩨ᩵}}, {{cog|tts|ซื่อ}} or {{m|tts|ซือ}}, {{cog|lo|ຊື່}}, {{cog|khb|ᦌᦹᧈ}}, {{cog|blt|ꪏꪳ꪿}}, {{cog|shn|သိုဝ်ႈ}}, {{cog|tdd|ᥔᥪ}}, {{cog|aho|𑜏𑜢𑜤𑜈𑜫}}, {{cog|zhn|swh}}.\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{za-pron}}\n\n===Adjective===\n{{za-head|adjective}}\n\n# [[straight]]"}}